Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这题考前猜到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这题也是轻轻松松解决
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.65,0:01:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯  最近很用功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.96,0:01:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.19,0:01:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起  日暮同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.69,0:01:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:55.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.20,0:01:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样高中入学考试也没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.36,0:01:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.10,0:02:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.04,0:02:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.71,0:02:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.23,0:02:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第57话\N一切源自桃源乡之夜  前篇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.94,0:02:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.17,0:02:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又要回国啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事用不着这么大声吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊  知道现在是什么时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.08,0:02:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道归知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我有很重要的模试呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸是?那什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.76,0:02:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,模拟试验  就是考试的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:03:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是什么“烤事”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  只要三天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.26,0:03:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想预习一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.27,0:03:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得戈薇姑娘也蛮辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:11.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直留在这里就轻松多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.77,0:03:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.74,0:03:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就那么喜欢那个\N叫“烤事”的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能会喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.71,0:03:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想回去故乡个三天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.09,0:03:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故乡?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要回驱魔师的村子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想修理飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为使用过度了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有三天喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  那我也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三天后我会到枫姥姥的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  云母
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.46,0:04:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算难得能好好休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚在就不能好好休息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉会答应的这么干脆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在看什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.41,0:04:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就快点回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是跑到这里的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.07,0:04:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饶了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得收你当弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.95,0:05:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然逃避修行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.08,0:05:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你讨厌风吹日晒\N与饿的前胸贴后背
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更不想最后被逼着上战场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.09,0:05:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像蝼蚁一般死去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说这些话的不是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饶…饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经对世间没有留恋了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才让你进入桃源乡\N修炼成为仙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不想当仙人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么可怕的地方我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事  好浓的雾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得这果实好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…人面果
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人面果?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是以人类作为养分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结出很像人脸的果实的妖树
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖树…就是妖怪树吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是会有这么多漂过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表示是相当大的树呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种时代
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来场大型战争
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.18,0:06:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肥料就多的用不完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种深山里会有战争吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  去调查看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是要回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正一定会在意的念不下书
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且考试是三天后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没闲功夫休息啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.71,0:07:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要无视我自己走掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别拖拖拉拉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是赶时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点解决掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人面果树就在这上面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这峭壁的上面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:47.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么巨大的人面果树
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.31,0:07:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是头一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这股不祥的妖气…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是用了很多人当养分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.96,0:07:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:07:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口气砍断那棵妖树
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们也帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.23,0:08:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到把你们一个个送到峭壁上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳都下山了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉一定打算
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在太阳下山前解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚是朔日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朔日…新月!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉的妖力会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成普通人类的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以犬夜叉才…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有长生不老的果实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老是这种东西连我都吃腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,养着这棵妖树吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.65,0:09:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没有感受到妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却散发出浓厚的死人臭味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呸  找我有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懒得跟你废话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.60,0:09:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要砍掉这棵怪异的树
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你胆敢阻碍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻碍你又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连你一起砍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.78,0:09:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对付这肥嘟嘟的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙起不了作用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就用风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道是打哪来的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你以为赢得了仙人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.98,0:10:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仙人?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.68,0:10:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我是桃源乡的仙人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桃果人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葫芦变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是  是你变小了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  这不是幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙真的是仙人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.01,0:10:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样的事别让我说太多遍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是仙人  为什么要这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  想要进来这里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只妖怪一定是上好的肥料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.53,0:10:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊  七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只差一点点了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  真让人刮目相看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到你的力气这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:10:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到今天是朔日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳下山以后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉就会变成普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:15.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子好像有人住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.37,0:11:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有其他人耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们住在这个地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么搞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.93,0:11:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂碎片变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,箱庭也变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.30,0:12:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是我们正在缩小
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.08,0:12:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.13,0:12:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是刚才在走路的小小男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.13,0:12:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是箱庭的内部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办啦\N我们也得住在这里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想个办法出去不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.34,0:12:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉会担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且四魂碎片也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.51,0:12:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.31,0:12:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还搞不清楚状况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.88,0:12:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先听听看这里的人怎么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问  大家在这里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:12:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里并非真实的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  有没有在听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.46,0:13:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别打扰我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们妨碍到修炼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.83,0:13:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修炼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在这做成为仙人的修炼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为仙人的修炼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要拥有仙人之力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.28,0:13:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.78,0:13:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能从桃果人大人那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:23.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到长生不老的人面果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.05,0:13:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桃果人?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是把你们\N困在这的罪魁祸首吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桃果人大人是将我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.06,0:13:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从饥饿与战乱之中\N救出来的大恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么看都只是生锈的刀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何那小子一挥\N就变成了大刀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  管他的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.33,0:14:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.39,0:14:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙已经掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我却没有妖化成妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来妖力已经减弱成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然被困在这种鬼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火鼠衣被…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.91,0:14:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子不能再拖下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只好从内部破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.49,0:14:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一点点伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浑蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有铁碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种东西才不放在眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个死胖子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我出去就把你大卸八块
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浑蛋!浑蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爪子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了  妖力消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.41,0:15:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还有两块
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.41,0:15:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这玩意儿只要有一块
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能让我的身体把刀子弹回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有了这些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是金刚不坏之身了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  愈来愈多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再拖下去会被溶化的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做那些事就能成为仙人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.01,0:16:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要拥有仙术
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确需要肉体的锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是精神方面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也必须更加强韧才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问  那边的诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来你们不是这里的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是武士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你似乎和其他人不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.70,0:16:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  其实没差多少
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我因为战败
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.77,0:16:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在逃到这个山谷的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.97,0:16:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被桃果人抓来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想成为仙人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.48,0:16:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我们会一点仙术的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.28,0:16:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就会变成人面果的养分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我亲眼看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桃果人与人面果在对话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.23,0:16:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人面果  还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:16:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没结出长生不老的果实吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.73,0:16:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还早着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再拿更多的仙人之魂来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.47,0:17:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仙人这东西  哪可能有那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只要照我的话做就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  人面果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很罗唆耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把这个拿下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就说不了话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住  住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我代你保管
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会把仙人之魂拿给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  战败的武士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.34,0:17:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进去吧!给我好好修行!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那很可能是四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很微弱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:18:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还是能感受到\N四魂碎片的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那家伙根本就是坏仙人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.07,0:18:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来  所谓的仙人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.07,0:18:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说如果没有舍弃世俗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.64,0:18:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入独特的境界的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.37,0:18:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是无法成为仙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这里的这些人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是无法成为仙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.65,0:18:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是为了成为人面果的肥料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而被强迫修行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙完全\N把我说的事情当耳边风
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也一起去告诉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了\N就算知道这些事也逃不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.90,0:18:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定有什么方法的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能逃得出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.67,0:18:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…你一定要平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.88,0:18:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变的会感觉到痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.08,0:18:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子已经变成普通人的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.69,0:19:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么样才能离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刀鞘在呼唤铁碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.20,0:19:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙一定在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.37,0:19:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  这样也许有用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  铁碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.71,0:19:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.93,0:19:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么搞的  这把烂刀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.47,0:19:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错没错  就是这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.75,0:20:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死胖子  觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.42,0:20:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是刚才那个妖怪小鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废话!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.69,0:20:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是还你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.89,0:20:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.70,0:20:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉碎片?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.77,0:20:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小子  找死!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.71,0:20:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死胖子  你是从哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼  该觉悟的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.52,0:21:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉碎片的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然够厉害!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.06,0:21:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.56,0:21:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么做才能逃离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.83,0:21:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时候犬夜叉一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.57,0:21:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到处都找不到出口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.54,0:21:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论走到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都只有墙壁而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.58,0:21:40.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不就成为仙人之后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.31,0:21:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成人面果的养分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.35,0:21:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不就这样在这里等死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这两种下场
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.59,0:21:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.29,0:21:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.29,0:21:54.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有任何梦想或希望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是梦就醒来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.94,0:22:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种恶梦我不想再做了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:30.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,除了真正珍贵的东西{\fad(500,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:42.18,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,若能全都舍弃 那该多好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.28,0:22:49.62,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,只是现实 往往是如此残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.59,0:22:53.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,但每当 遇到这种时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.36,0:22:58.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要紧闭双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.10,0:23:05.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,便能看见 你的笑容{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.67,0:23:12.31,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah- 但愿从此以往
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.15,0:23:19.89,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,直到进入 沉眠的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.62,0:23:27.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,你的 那抹笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.03,0:23:35.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,都绝没有 消逝的瞬间{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.14,0:23:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是梦  一定是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.11,0:23:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  捏我一下看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.31,0:23:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…果然不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.18,0:23:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你现在因为朔日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.32,0:23:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而变成了普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.92,0:24:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能打赢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.85,0:24:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个施展怪异仙术的桃果人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.62,0:24:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要为了我舍命?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.96,0:24:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  不行啊  犬夜叉!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.40,0:24:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.70,0:24:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切源自桃源乡之夜  后篇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.27,0:24:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黎明…快点来临吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.40,0:24:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉宝典
